title: Commerical Kitchen, Party Room & Home for Sale 16299 US
text:
Commerical Kitchen, Party Room & Home for Sale 16299 US ad date: 10/17/2015 
Commerical Kitchen, Party Room & Home for Sale 16299 US Hwy 101 North, Smith River, CA Beautiful French tudor revival home built in the late 1930's. 4,681 sq.ft. of living space with a lot of original features and numerous updated features too! Old style kitchen, large pantry, built-ins, formal living and dining rooms, new hardwood flooring, fireplace with propane log insert and terrace with ocean views. A large commercial kitchen & "party room" with bar adjoin the residence for reputable "Fabulous Food by Julie" catering business, & equipment too. Check it out @ www.smithrivercahomeandcatering.com No. 1264059 $449,000
